data.description: Discover the epitome of pure elegance and sophistication. With 6,486 of living space this beauty boasts 6 extraordinary BR's, 5 1/2Baths. 2 laundry rooms, Thermador appliances. The heart of this home lies in the beautiful open kitchen and windows to showcase the luxurious RH light fixtures. 10 ft ceilings down, 9ft up on 1.74 acre lot w/private pond and massive stone covered patio is ideal for family gatherings. This location is prime with much more to see in person. Open House Sun 12/17 2-3:30p
